questionsAndAnswers.question: What makes you unique among Pro designers?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: With 10+ years in UX/UI design, I‚Äôve worked with top brands like Seat, KFC, Xiaomi, and Microsoft. I focus on user-centric designs, collaborating closely with clients to create intuitive interfaces that enhance user experience and reflect their unique needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is a Fiverr PRO seller?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A seller who meets the Fiverr Pro standards will have a Pro badge added to their profile. Every Pro Gig is labeled with a Pro badge so that buyers know they're getting the very best.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is a revision?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A revision stands as a step forward in the evolution of the initial concept or ongoing design, responding to client input, feedback, or necessary adjustments to advance towards the final product. Each revision encompasses the integration of all requested modifications onto the most recent design ite

questionsAndAnswers.question: I need an amount of screen/page more than in the package, can you still do them?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, just message me and let me know how many screens you need to design. I will send you a custom offer.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Refund Policy
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I offer a no-questions-asked full refund if, during the homepage draft phase, you feel I'm not the right fit for your design needs. Please note: This refund policy applies exclusively to the initial homepage draft stage, prior to any revisions being made.
